# 🍎 Kleopatra for macOS — KDE 6 Version

Welcome to the **Homebrew Tap for Kleopatra v24**, the modern KDE 6-based version of Gpg4win's certificate manager and OpenPGP frontend — now available for macOS!

This tap makes it easy to install the latest KDE 6 version of Kleopatra via Homebrew.

## 🔧 Installation

First, tap the repository:

```bash
brew tap theapplegates/kleopatra-mac-v24
